### POST /api/profiles - Create a new profile
POST http://localhost:3000/api/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ella"
}

### POST /api/profiles - Test idempotency (same name)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ella"
}

### GET /api/profiles/{id} - Get profile by ID (replace {id} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/profiles/{}

### GET /api/profiles - Get all profiles
GET http://localhost:3000/api/profiles

### GET /api/profiles - Get profiles with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/profiles?gender=female&country_id=US

### DELETE /api/profiles/{id} - Delete profile by ID (replace {id} with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/profiles/{id}

### Test bad request - Missing name
POST http://localhost:3000/api/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test bad request - Empty name
POST http://localhost:3000/api/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}


